collector.data
Class Field

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--collector.data.Field
All Implemented Interfaces:
Element
public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
implements Element

A Field is the basic component of the header of a Table.

  • label : name of the field
  • typeField : type of Data
  • index : rank in the referenceTable A Field can inherit from one other Field. None by default.
